                                </p>
                                <div class="userAgreementsTextContainer">
                                    <input class="agreementInput" type="checkbox" required>
                                    </input>
                                    <p class="agreeemntsText">
                                        Yes I am 13 and allowed to use this site.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <p class="agreeemntsText">
                                    Please <em>read</em> <strong>and</strong> <em>accept</em>
